   <Ritual>
      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>VrS77.39 Var. a (mss. 2005, 2007, 2109):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            <em>imat̰ barəsma</em> ēn gyāg barsom az māhrōy abāz wišādan ō ī māhrōy nihišn pas <em>haδa.zaōθrəm haδa.aiβiiā̊ŋhəm</em>.</ab> 
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "<em>imat̰ barəsma</em>. At this passage he has to release the <em>barsom</em> from the <em>māhrōy</em> and put it on to the <em>māhrōy</em>. Afterwards (he has to continue with) 
            <em>haδa.zaōθrəm haδa.aiβiiā̊ŋhəm</em>."</ab>
         
         <ab>VrS77.39 Var. b (mss. 2010, 2030, 2040, 2104, 2109):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            <em>imat̰ barəsma</em> ēn gyāg barsom az māhrōy gušādan ud datuš abāg gyāg kardan pas <em>haδa.zaōθrəm haδa.aiβiiā̊ŋhəm</em>.</ab>  
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "<em>imat̰ barəsma</em>. At this passage, he should release the <em>barsom</em> from the <em>māhrōy</em> and put the <em>datuš</em> back to its place. Afterwards (he has to 
            continue with) <em>haδa.zaōθrəm haδa.aiβiiā̊ŋhəm</em>."</ab>
      </Nerangs>
